				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">$2003←4×Cur $2004←Y[Cur] $2004←Cur $2004←Cur&amp;3 $2004←X[Cur]<br /><br />RS : finishes with $2003←0<br />ST : finishes with $2003←$FF $2004←X[$3F]</div><br /><br />I'm assuming that notation translates to the following code:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">LDA cur<br />ASL A<br />ASL A<br />STA $2003<br /><br />TAX<br />LDA oam,X<br />STA $2004<br /><br />LDA cur<br />STA $2004<br /><br />AND #$03<br />STA $2004<br /><br />LDA oam+3,X<br />STA $2004<br /><br />RS:<br />LDA #$00<br />STA $2003<br /><br />ST:<br />LDA #$FF<br />STA $2003<br /><br />LDA oam+$FF<br />STA $2004<br /></div></div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
